msgstr "Izberite raven povečave"

#. Translators: "Not applicable" string for the media properties dialog when a
#. given property is unknown or missing (e.g. images don't have frame rate).
#: src/page.rs:274 src/window.rs:475 src/window.rs:483 src/window.rs:491
msgid "N/A"
msgstr "N/D"

#: src/window.rs:335
msgid "Added row and column tiled display modes for side-by-side comparison."
msgstr "Dodani načini prikaza v vrsticah in stolpcih za primerjavo."

#: src/window.rs:336
msgid ""
"Changed mouse scroll and hotkey zoom to have consistent speed regardless of "
"the current zoom level."
msgstr ""
"Spremenjeno drsenje miške in povečava s hitrimi tipkami, da imajo dosledno "
"hitrost ne glede na trenutno raven povečave."

#: src/window.rs:337
msgid ""
"Changed mouse scroll to zoom by default instead of panning, and to pan when "
"Ctrl is held."
msgstr ""
"Spremenjeno drsenje miške za privzeto povečavo namesto pomikanja ter "
"pomikanje, ko je krmilka pritisnjena."

#: src/window.rs:338
msgid ""
"Added panning by holding down the left mouse button and dragging when zoomed-"
"in."
msgstr ""
"Dodano pomikanje, da držite levi gumb miške in povlečete, ko približate "
"pogled."

#: src/window.rs:339
msgid "Changed the playback position to update smoothly."
msgstr "Spremenjen položaj predvajanja, da se nemoteno posodobi."

#: src/window.rs:340
msgid ""
"You can now drag-and-drop a file out of Identity when it is not zoomed-in."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj lahko datoteko povlečete in spustite iz programa Istovetnost, ko ni "
"povečana."

#: src/window.rs:341
msgid "Added Ctrl+C to copy the current file to clipboard."
msgstr "Dodana bližnjica krmilka+C za kopiranje trenutne datoteke v odložišče."

#: src/window.rs:342
msgid "Added a context menu to tabs with a few common actions."
msgstr "Zavihkom je dodan kontekstni meni z nekaj pogostimi dejanji."

#: src/window.rs:343
msgid ""
"Optimized video playback performance by enabling OpenGL video processing on "
"compatible setups."
msgstr ""
"Optimizirana učinkovitost predvajanja videoposnetkov z omogočanjem obdelave "
"videoposnetkov OpenGL na združljivih sistemih."

#: src/window.rs:344
msgid "Updated to the GNOME 44 platform."
msgstr "Posodobljeno na platformo GNOME 44."

#: src/window.rs:345
msgid "Updated translations."
msgstr "Posodobljeni prevodi."

#: src/window.rs:348
msgid ""
"This release adds row and column display modes, reworks mouse gestures and "
"adds drag-and-drop from Identity."
msgstr ""
"Ta izdaja dodaja načine prikaza v vrsticah in stolpcih, vsebuje predelane "
"poteze miške ter dodaja funkcijo povleci-in-spusti iz programa Istovetnost."

